body:
In [[Bleach]], bankai is the second and final form that a [[zanpakutou]] can take, being more more powerful than a [[shikai]] and with a more drastic change in appearance. It requires a lot of experience to unlock so only the higher ranking members of the shinigamis are able to unleash it. Like shikai, a user is able to release and revert their bankai at will.

h4. Related searches

* {{kurosaki_ichigo bankai}}
* {{kuchiki_byakuya bankai}}
* {{sui-feng bankai}}
* {{hitsugaya_toushirou bankai}}
* etc.

h4. See also

* [[Shikai]]
* [[resurreccion|Resurrección]]

In [[Bleach]], shikai is the first form and special ability of a [[zanpakutou]]. Each individual has their own unique shikai with their own appearance and abilities. Users are usually able to release and revert their shikai at will, though some individuals have a "full-time release" shikai where their sword is always in shikai form.

A shikai is less powerful than the second and final form, [[bankai]].

